# Entities

Game objects and entity classes.

## Files to Create

- **Player.lua** - Player mecha entity
- **Enemy.lua** - Base enemy class
- **Bullet.lua** - Bullet/projectile entity
- **PowerUp.lua** - Power-up collectibles
- **Boss.lua** - Boss enemy class
- **Explosion.lua** - Explosion effect entity

Ask @gameplay to implement the player and enemy entities!
